metadata.name: The I.T. Ninja
metadata.description:
The Information Technology Ninja, or the I.T. NINJA. This is what most people in the I.T. departments feel like at times. With satire, humor, pop culture references thrown in to try and elevate to a level of art beyond mere illustration.
If work in the I.T. department and you don't relate to this, don't worry about it, you're probably just an I.T. Guru, your Co-worker, he's the Ninja....
